---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Speaking"
  description="Christian Kameir speaks on the future of money, blockchain investing, decentralized finance, and digital identity. Keynotes, conference sessions, and expert panels. Fees from $1,950."
>
  <article class="speaking">
    <div class="container">

      <!-- ── Header ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <header class="speaking__header">
        <p class="label">Speaking</p>
        <h1 class="speaking__title">The room needs a different frame<br>on the money question.</h1>
        <p class="speaking__intro">
          Thirty years across capital markets, technology, and law —
          including active roles in CBDC development, decentralized identity
          infrastructure, and venture investing across three continents.
          Kameir does not speak from the sidelines.
        </p>
      </header>

      <hr class="rule" />

      <!-- ── Topics ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <section class="speaking__section">
        <h2 class="speaking__section-title">Speaking topics</h2>

        <div class="topic">
          <div class="topic__head">
            <span class="topic__number">01</span>
            <h3 class="topic__name">The State of Blockchain</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="topic__desc">
            The blockchain space is a rapidly evolving paradigm reshaping finance,
            supply chain, identity, and more. As managing partner of a venture fund
            that evaluates hundreds of blockchain projects each year — applying a
            rigorous, peer-reviewed investment process — Kameir is in the position
            to deliver a comprehensive, signal-over-noise view of where the technology
            actually stands and where it is going.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="topic">
          <div class="topic__head">
            <span class="topic__number">02</span>
            <h3 class="topic__name">Investing into Decentralized Finance</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="topic__desc">
            Blockchain and decentralized finance solutions offer investment opportunities
            that exceed those of previous technology advances — yet the space is flooded
            with jargon and marketing material that makes it hard to develop actionable
            criteria. This session applies sound technology investor principles and
            deep industry expertise to answer the question that matters: what makes a
            project in this space actually investable?
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="topic">
          <div class="topic__head">
            <span class="topic__number">03</span>
            <h3 class="topic__name">The Future of Money</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="topic__desc">
            The technology underpinning global financial systems is undergoing the most
            significant paradigm shift since the introduction of computers. Central banks
            of all developed nations are actively researching or building new currency
            technologies. As an active participant in CBDC development and an investor
            in the technologies supporting next-generation monetary solutions, Kameir
            provides the most current, practitioner-level overview of where money is going
            — and what it means for your industry.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="topic">
          <div class="topic__head">
            <span class="topic__number">04</span>
            <h3 class="topic__name">Blockchain and the Security of Personal Data</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="topic__desc">
            Cybercrime costs individuals and businesses an estimated $500 billion annually.
            California, Texas, Nevada, Washington, and New York have all moved toward
            GDPR-style data protection frameworks — and a new generation of tools is
            emerging to address the underlying risks. With a background spanning technology,
            law, and venture investing, and as an early investor in decentralized identity
            with advanced biometrics, Kameir presents the practical state of the art in
            personal data security and what organizations need to understand now.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="topic__custom">
          Event- and organization-specific topics are available on request.
          Additional subjects can be drawn from Kameir's writing at
          <a href="https://forbes.kameir.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Forbes</a>
          and <a href="https://hackernoon.com/@kameir" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HackerNoon</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <hr class="rule" />

      <!-- ── Past engagements ────────────────────────────── -->
      <section class="speaking__section">
        <h2 class="speaking__section-title">Selected past engagements</h2>
        <ol class="engagements__list" role="list">
          <li class="engagements__item">
            <a href="https://oneworldidentity.com/podcast/sustanycapital/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="engagements__link">
              <span class="engagements__name">DIVI Podcast</span>
              <span class="engagements__detail">The State of Central Bank Digital Currencies</span>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="engagements__item">
            <a href="https://bit.ly/3i7exX1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="engagements__link">
              <span class="engagements__name">Mikobits Podcast</span>
              <span class="engagements__detail">Thesis Investing</span>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="engagements__item">
            <a href="https://youtu.be/C82nUbyzbso" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="engagements__link">
              <span class="engagements__name">Unblockable Podcast</span>
              <span class="engagements__detail">The State of Money</span>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="engagements__item">
            <a href="https://apple.co/3mWy3Zz" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="engagements__link">
              <span class="engagements__name">Block52 Podcast</span>
              <span class="engagements__detail">Programmable Euro and Beyond</span>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="engagements__item">
            <a href="https://youtu.be/0-Lw9zp55Jk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="engagements__link">
              <span class="engagements__name">Keynote — IDEAS Conference</span>
              <span class="engagements__detail">The Future of Fintech</span>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="engagements__item">
            <a href="https://youtu.be/neV9Mz6oOkk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="engagements__link">
              <span class="engagements__name">Expert Panel</span>
              <span class="engagements__detail">Alternative Funding</span>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="engagements__item">
            <a href="https://youtu.be/brzLTA2q6qs" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="engagements__link">
              <span class="engagements__name">Keynote — OnChain Conference</span>
              <span class="engagements__detail">Blockchain Investing</span>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="engagements__item">
            <a href="https://youtu.be/F3two0v84JI" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="engagements__link">
              <span class="engagements__name">Keynote — Web3 Conference</span>
              <span class="engagements__detail"></span>
            </a>
          </li>
        </ol>
        <p class="engagements__more">
          Full list of articles, podcasts, and events:
          <a href="https://sustany.co/press.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">sustany.co/press</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <hr class="rule" />

      <!-- ── Fees ────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <section class="speaking__section">
        <h2 class="speaking__section-title">Fees</h2>

        <div class="fees__grid">
          <div class="fees__col">
            <p class="fees__format-label">In person</p>
            <div class="fees__row">
              <span class="fees__region">United States</span>
              <span class="fees__amount">$6,950 + travel</span>
            </div>
            <div class="fees__row">
              <span class="fees__region">Europe</span>
              <span class="fees__amount">$11,950 + travel</span>
            </div>
            <div class="fees__row">
              <span class="fees__region">Middle East &amp; Asia</span>
              <span class="fees__amount">$13,950 + travel</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="fees__col">
            <p class="fees__format-label">Virtual</p>
            <div class="fees__row">
              <span class="fees__region">All regions</span>
              <span class="fees__amount">$1,950</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="fees__note">
          Additional costs may apply for organization- or industry-specific engagements.
          Fees may be reduced or waived for educational events and non-profit organizations.
        </p>
      </section>

      <hr class="rule" />

      <!-- ── CTA ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <section class="speaking__cta">
        <p class="speaking__cta-text">
          To check availability, discuss a topic, or request a booking, use the
          contact form. Include the event name, date, location, and expected audience.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Request a booking</a>
      </section>

    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
/* ── Header ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.speaking__header {
  padding-top: 4rem;
  padding-bottom: var(--space-l);
}

.speaking__title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.25rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  margin-top: 0.75rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}

.speaking__intro {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  max-width: 560px;
  line-height: 1.75;
}

/* ── Sections ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.speaking__section {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-l);
}

.speaking__section-title {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
}

/* ── Topics ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.topic {
  padding-bottom: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.topic:last-of-type {
  border-bottom: none;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.topic__head {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.topic__number {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.topic__name {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--text);
  margin: 0;
}

.topic__desc {
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: var(--text);
  max-width: 640px;
}

.topic__custom {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.7;
  max-width: 560px;
  padding-top: 0.5rem;
}

/* ── Past engagements ─────────────────────────────────────── */
.engagements__list {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
}

.engagements__item {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
}

.engagements__item:last-child {
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
}

.engagements__link {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  padding-block: 0.9rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: inherit;
  transition: color 0.15s, padding-left 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
  border-left: 2px solid transparent;
  margin-left: -2px;
}

.engagements__link:hover {
  color: var(--accent);
  padding-left: 0.75rem;
  border-left-color: var(--accent);
}

.engagements__name {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  min-width: 220px;
}

.engagements__detail {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
}

.engagements__more {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-top: 1.25rem;
}

/* ── Fees ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.fees__grid {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-xl);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.fees__format-label {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.fees__row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 2rem;
  align-items: baseline;
  padding-block: 0.55rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
}

.fees__row:first-of-type {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
}

.fees__region {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--text);
  min-width: 160px;
}

.fees__amount {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text);
  letter-spacing: 0.01em;
}

.fees__note {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.7;
  max-width: 560px;
}

/* ── CTA ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.speaking__cta {
  padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
}

.speaking__cta-text {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  max-width: 520px;
  line-height: 1.75;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-m);
}

/* ── Responsive ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .engagements__link {
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin-left: 0;
    border-left: none;
    border-top: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: border-top-color 0.15s, color 0.15s;
  }

  .engagements__link:hover {
    padding-left: 0;
    border-left: none;
    border-top-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .engagements__name {
    min-width: unset;
  }

  .fees__grid {
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-l);
  }
}
</style>
